parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can cause the passenger or driver to be unrestrained in the event of sudden stops or accidents, leading to increased risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle does not lock
the seat belt buckle is broken
the seat belt fails to restrain the passenger or driver
the seat belt buckle sometimes works and sometimes does not.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delayed notification of the recall concerning seat belt buckles can lead to a prolonged period of risk for passengers and drivers, as they may be unaware of the potential safety issue.
symptoms: Excessive time taken by the manufacturer to notify owners of the recall
lack of timely notification of the recall.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents, loss of control, or stranding the driver.
symptoms: the vehicle loses power or acceleration
the transmission makes unusual noises or vibrations
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear
the transmission warning light illuminates on the dashboard.
